zone.note: The flower studs seem to be symmetrically placed.
Stippling is scattered throughout the piece. This might be to stabalize symmetry.

div.p: Verscheyden Nvwe Compartamenten voor alle constenaers, als platsnyders en schilders goutsmeeden beeltsnyders kistemakers metselders, etc. seer nut ende dienstlycken. WOLTER SWEERSZ DROLLICH INVENTOR Jaques goltzius exc

Diverse new compartments for all artists, including plate cutters and painters, goldsmiths, sculptors, joiners, masons, etc. Very useful and helpful. Invented by Wolter Sweersz. Drollich. Published by Jacob II Goltzius.
